attributes.Long form description: The student wants to disassemble the furniture so he first unscrews the first leg of the table. He then unscrews and removes the second leg. Next, the student disassembles the first and third legs and removes the shelf of the table. Finally, he disassembles the last leg.

attributes.Action sentence: The student unscrews the first leg from the shelf.
The student unscrews the second leg from the shelf.
The student disassembles the second leg.
The student disassembles the first leg.
The student disassembles the third leg.
The student disassembles the fourth leg.
